title: Chung Shan Industrial and Commercial School
text: The Chung Shan Industrial and Commercial School (CSIC; ) is a <a href="vocational%20school">vocational school</a> in <a href="Daliao%20District">Daliao District</a>, <a href="Kaohsiung">Kaohsiung</a>, <a href="Taiwan">Taiwan</a>. Furthermore, the school also famous for <a href="association%20football">football</a> and <a href="volleyball">volleyball</a> in Taiwan.
